longBusinessSummary: Alltronics Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and trades in electronic products, plastic moulds, and plastics and other components for electronic products in the United States, Hong Kong, Europe, the People's Republic of China, and internationally. The company operates through three segments: Electronic Products, Biodiesel Products, and Energy Saving Business. It also offers home improvement electronic products, such as irrigation controllers, aroma ionizers, radio controlled clocks, clock movement units, battery chargers, corded phones, and carbon monoxide detectors; and transformers, solenoids, inductors, and adapters, as well as walkie-talki products. In addition, the company engages in the trading of biodiesel products; and the provision of energy saving business solutions, as well as energy efficient gas stoves. The company was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Hong Kong, Hong Kong.
